<div style="text-align: center;">
<blockquote>
<p>Hello there. I see you've somehow managed to stumble upon this page.<br />
I suppose now you're wondering why you're here.<br />
Well, to be frank, I have no idea.<br />
I don't even know how I got here myself.<br />
But since you are here, feel free to browse my collection.</p>
<p>There might even be a good article or two in here.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
