<div id="wiki-tabview-7ac399e641f70b9b53dbb7d5456ab86f" class="yui-navset">
<ul class="yui-nav">
<li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>The Man behind the strange</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Things I've Written</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Current Works</em></a></li>
</ul>
<div class="yui-content">
<div id="wiki-tab-0-0">
<p>Ah yes, you've come to know more. Very good indeed, let's not dilly dally.</p>
<p>I was born in a wee little town in New Jersey and have been all over the east coast of the United States. Currently I'm nested in an even smaller town in upstate New York.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Some&nbsp;Personal&nbsp;Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Close</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Okay, so I have a tendency to talk about myself for far longer than I should so let's get to the good stuff.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Item #:</strong> Marcelles Diablo Raynes</p>
<p><strong>Object Class:</strong> Bisexual</p>
<p><strong>Special Containment Procedures:</strong> Due to the sheer amount of fuckery I am capable of, I cannot be properly contained. Fruit snacks are my favourite food and will serve as an excellent distraction.</p>
<p><strong>Description:</strong> Hello, I'm Marcelles D. Raynes (Name pending), welcome to the &quot;About Me&quot; section. I'm 22 (Age Pending) and a father to one little baby boy. I enjoy writing and reading, hence why I'm a part of this site! I vastly prefer Tales and GoI stuff as opposed to SCP articles though, fun fact, and I absolutely love canons.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Outside of the wiki, I'm still a writer. I'm currently working on a book called &quot;The White Ashes&quot;, and have a pretty decent understanding about graphic design. <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/the-radical-works-of-marcelles-d-raynes">Check out this page</a> to see some of the things I've created!</p>
</div>
